I am extremely sorry if my comment hurts the sentiments of anyone. But my intention is not bad.
Let me tell the reality that in the vision of most of the Indians the image of Pakistan as a country is very bad and dishonourable because of many political and diplomatic reasons. But music is the platform in which, i think, we should put aside our personal grudges and try to improve our relationships by admiring each other. And i personally accept that you guys excel us as most of the gems of music are on your side.
Don't take it otherwise people, its not comparison but its my respect for your excellence in music.
Thanks...
